---
import { Card, CardGrid } from '@astrojs/starlight/components';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Peri — 更小、更快、任何模型</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Peri 是一个 Rust 编写的编码助手。13MB 二进制，~50MB 内存，98% 缓存命中。支持 DeepSeek、GLM、Qwen、Anthropic 等任何模型。" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,600;0,9..144,700;1,9..144,300&family=Figtree:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <svg style="position:absolute;width:0;height:0" aria-hidden="true">
      <defs>
        <filter id="caustic" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%">
          <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.015 0.012" numOctaves="3" seed="2" result="noise" />
          <feColorMatrix type="matrix" values="0 0 0 0 0.82  0 0 0 0 0.88  0 0 0 0 0.91  0 0 0 0.18 0" in="noise" result="colored" />
          <feComposite operator="in" in="colored" in2="SourceGraphic" result="comp" />
          <feBlend mode="overlay" in="comp" in2="SourceGraphic" />
        </filter>
        <filter id="grain">
          <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.65" numOctaves="1" stitchTiles="stitch" />
          <feColorMatrix type="saturate" values="0" />
          <feBlend mode="multiply" in="SourceGraphic" in2="result1" result="grain" />
        </filter>
      </defs>
    </svg>

    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

      body {
        font-family: 'Figtree', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        background: #faf7f2;
        color: #1a1816;
        line-height: 1.7;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      /* ============================================
         Navigation
         ============================================ */
      .nav {
        position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
        background: transparent;
        transition: background 0.3s ease, backdrop-filter 0.3s ease;
      }
      .nav.scrolled {
        background: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.82);
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(91, 164, 188, 0.12);
      }
      .nav-logo {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a3a4a;
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
      .nav-links a {
        text-decoration: none; color: #3d3833; font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 0.95rem; transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .nav-links a:hover { color: #5ba4bc; }

      /* ============================================
         Hero
         ============================================ */
      .hero {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex; flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      /* Caustic light blobs */
      .caustic-layer {
        position: absolute; inset: 0;
        pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
      }
      .caustic-blob {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 63% 37% 54% 46% / 44% 58% 42% 56%;
        filter: blur(60px);
        opacity: 0.25;
        animation: drift 18s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      .caustic-blob:nth-child(1) {
        width: 55vmax; height: 55vmax;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 40% 50%, #d8edf4, transparent 70%);
        top: -20%; left: -15%;
        animation-delay: 0s;
      }
      .caustic-blob:nth-child(2) {
        width: 45vmax; height: 45vmax;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 60% 40%, #bce0ed, transparent 70%);
        top: 10%; right: -10%;
        animation-delay: -6s;
        border-radius: 51% 49% 62% 38% / 58% 40% 60% 42%;
      }
      .caustic-blob:nth-child(3) {
        width: 38vmax; height: 38vmax;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 60%, #e8d5a3, transparent 70%);
        bottom: -10%; left: 30%;
        animation-delay: -12s;
      }
      .caustic-blob:nth-child(4) {
        width: 30vmax; height: 30vmax;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 65% 55%, #c8dfe8, transparent 70%);
        top: 40%; right: 25%;
        animation-delay: -3s;
      }

      @keyframes drift {
        0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1) rotate(0deg); }
        25% { transform: translate(3%, -2%) scale(1.08) rotate(1deg); }
        50% { transform: translate(-1%, 3%) scale(0.94) rotate(-1deg); }
        75% { transform: translate(-3%, -1%) scale(1.05) rotate(0.5deg); }
      }

      /* Grain overlay */
      .grain-overlay {
        position: absolute; inset: 0;
        pointer-events: none; z-index: 1; opacity: 0.06;
        background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.7' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        background-size: 256px;
      }

      .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 820px; }

      .hero-eyebrow {
        font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase; color: #5ba4bc;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out both;
        animation-delay: 0.1s;
      }
      .hero-title {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 8vw, 6rem);
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.05;
        color: #1a3a4a;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out both;
        animation-delay: 0.2s;
      }
      .hero-title em {
        font-style: italic;
        color: #5ba4bc;
      }
      .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
        color: #6b6560;
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.6;
        animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out both;
        animation-delay: 0.35s;
      }
      .hero-actions {
        display: flex; gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
        animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out both;
        animation-delay: 0.5s;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
        border-radius: 2rem;
        font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        cursor: pointer; border: none;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        background: #1a3a4a; color: #faf7f2;
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        background: #274a5c;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(26, 58, 74, 0.25);
      }
      .btn-outline {
        background: transparent;
        color: #1a3a4a;
        border: 1.5px solid #1a3a4a;
      }
      .btn-outline:hover {
        background: rgba(26, 58, 74, 0.06);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      @keyframes fadeUp {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
      }

      /* ============================================
         Stats Bar
         ============================================ */
      .stats {
        position: relative; z-index: 3;
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: -3rem auto 4rem;
        padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
        display: flex; justify-content: space-around;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(91, 164, 188, 0.15);
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(91, 164, 188, 0.06);
      }
      .stat-item {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
      }
      .stat-item + .stat-item {
        border-left: 1px solid rgba(91, 164, 188, 0.2);
      }
      .stat-num {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
        font-weight: 600; color: #1a3a4a;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      .stat-label {
        font-size: 0.8rem; color: #6b6560;
        font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
      }

      /* ============================================
         Features
         ============================================ */
      .features {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;
        position: relative; z-index: 2;
      }
      .section-heading {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
        font-weight: 400; color: #1a3a4a;
        text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      .section-sub {
        text-align: center; color: #6b6560;
        font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }
      .feature-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .feature-card {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(91, 164, 188, 0.12);
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        transition: all 0.35s ease;
        position: relative;
      }
      .feature-card:nth-child(1) { border-radius: 60% 40% 50% 50% / 45% 55% 45% 55%; }
      .feature-card:nth-child(2) { border-radius: 40% 60% 55% 45% / 55% 45% 55% 45%; }
      .feature-card:nth-child(3) { border-radius: 50% 50% 40% 60% / 50% 50% 60% 40%; }
      .feature-card:nth-child(4) { border-radius: 45% 55% 60% 40% / 40% 60% 45% 55%; }
      .feature-card:nth-child(5) { border-radius: 55% 45% 40% 60% / 60% 40% 55% 45%; }
      .feature-card:nth-child(6) { border-radius: 50% 50% 55% 45% / 45% 55% 50% 50%; }

      .feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(91, 164, 188, 0.15);
        border-color: rgba(91, 164, 188, 0.3);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      }
      .feature-icon {
        font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block;
      }
      .feature-title {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 500;
        color: #1a3a4a; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      }
      .feature-desc {
        font-size: 0.92rem; color: #6b6560; line-height: 1.55;
      }

      /* ============================================
         CTA
         ============================================ */
      .cta {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 5rem 2rem 6rem;
        position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      }
      .cta::before {
        content: ''; position: absolute;
        inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
        background:
          radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 30% 50%, rgba(216, 237, 244, 0.35), transparent),
          radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 70% 40%, rgba(188, 224, 237, 0.25), transparent);
      }
      .cta-content {
        position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .cta-title {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
        font-weight: 400; color: #1a3a4a;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .cta-desc {
        color: #6b6560; margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      /* ============================================
         Footer
         ============================================ */
      .footer {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(91, 164, 188, 0.15);
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: #a0988c;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .footer a { color: #5ba4bc; text-decoration: none; }
      .footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

      /* ============================================
         Responsive
         ============================================ */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; }
        .stat-item + .stat-item { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(91,164,188,0.2); padding-top: 1rem; }
        .nav-links { gap: 1.2rem; }
      }
    </style>

    <script>
      // Navbar scroll effect
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        const nav = document.querySelector('.nav');
        const onScroll = () => nav?.classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 40);
        window.addEventListener('scroll', onScroll, { passive: true });
      });
    </script>

    <!-- ============ Navigation ============ -->
    <nav class="nav" aria-label="主导航">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Peri</a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/docs/get-started/introduction/">文档</a></li>
        <li><a href="/posts/engineering/demo-context-budget/">工程</a></li>
        <li><a href="/posts/product/demo-introducing-peri/">产品</a></li>
        <li><a href="/posts/research/demo-domestic-models/">研究</a></li>
        <li><a href="/posts/news/demo-v2-release/">动态</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/konghayao/peri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- ============ Hero ============ -->
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
      <div class="caustic-layer">
        <div class="caustic-blob"></div>
        <div class="caustic-blob"></div>
        <div class="caustic-blob"></div>
        <div class="caustic-blob"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grain-overlay"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">Rust 编写 · 任何模型 · 零迁移</p>
        <h1 id="hero-title" class="hero-title">更小<em>更快</em>更自由</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Peri 是一个用 Rust 从头构建的编码助手，兼容 Claude Code 的生态。
          一个 13MB 的二进制文件，一块 ~50MB 的内存，一份 98% 缓存命的智能。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/guides/getting-started/" class="btn btn-primary">
            快速开始 →
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/konghayao/peri" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ Stats ============ -->
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">13 MB</div>
        <div class="stat-label">二进制体积</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">~50 MB</div>
        <div class="stat-label">运行时内存</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">98%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">缓存命中率</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ Features ============ -->
    <section class="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
      <h2 id="features-heading" class="section-heading">为什么选择 Peri</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">不是又一个 AI 工具，是一个更轻、更快、更开放的编码平台。</p>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">🦀</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Rust 构建，非 Node.js</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">13MB 二进制，~50MB 内存。永远不会在你没注意时偷偷涨到 1GB。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">⚡</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">95–99% 缓存命中</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">冻结系统提示词 + 边界标记机制，最大限度减少浪费的 token。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">🌐</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">任何 LLM，自由切换</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">DeepSeek、GLM、Qwen、Anthropic、OpenAI——会话中随时切换，无需重启。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">🔌</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">零迁移，今日即用</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">你现有的 Claude Code 配置直接能用。Skills、Hooks、MCP、插件——一切都兼容。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">🤖</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">内置智能子代理</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">7 个专业子代理：编码、探索、代码审查、Web 研究……把任务分派到后台，继续你的工作。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">📦</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">AGM 包管理器</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">agm install 任何 skill 或 agent。一把锁文件，所有工具互通。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA ============ -->
    <section class="cta">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2 class="cta-title">准备好了吗？</h2>
        <p class="cta-desc">
          一条命令安装，无需编辑任何配置文件。第一次启动会引导你完成模型和 API Key 的配置。
        </p>
        <code style="display:block;background:#1a1816;color:#c8dfe8;padding:1rem 1.5rem;border-radius:1rem;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-family:'SF Mono','Fira Code',monospace;">
          curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/konghayao/peri/main/scripts/install.sh | bash
        </code>
        <a href="/guides/getting-started/" class="btn btn-primary">查看完整指南 →</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ Footer ============ -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <p>由 <a href="https://github.com/konghayao/peri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Peri</a> 团队构建 · 
      <a href="https://github.com/konghayao/peri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a> · 
      Apache 2.0 许可证</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
